HEADWORD: Pistillate
<hw>Pis"til*late</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Having a pistil or pistils; -- usually said of flowers having
pistils but no stamens.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

